      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aTV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 569293735,
      "version": 928,
      "versionNonce": 1553398471,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772375859185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Inside DRDY interrupt\ncallback:\n- Combine 3 bytes in uint32_t\nvariable.\n- Write to uint32_t ring\nbuffer.\nInside USB CDC_Receive_FS:\n- memmov recieved data\n- Set DATA_READY status\nInside main loop:\n- Take value from ring buffer\n(maybe wait for half-full\nbuffer -> take half of\nbuffer) also stop conversion\nif buffer is full.\n- TX data from ring buffer to\nPC.\n- If DATA_READY, start\ncommand processing using\nstate machine.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "uwmFJgOBLBnVD59kbV1i6",
      "originalText": "Inside DRDY interrupt callback:\n- Combine 3 bytes in uint32_t variable.\n- Write to uint32_t ring buffer.\nInside USB CDC_Receive_FS:\n- memmov recieved data\n- Set DATA_READY status\nInside main loop:\n- Take value from ring buffer (maybe wait for half-full buffer -> take half of buffer) also stop conversion if buffer is full.\n- TX data from ring buffer to PC.\n- If DATA_READY, start command processing using state machine.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
